• Rails

    - Global 

        rails routes
        rails console
        rails console — sandbox : ne persiste aucun changement
        
        docker-compose run web rails c
        docker exec ...

            > rails console
                > ActiveRecord::Base.connection.tables : affiche tables

            > rails db:console
                >

        > rails db:migrate
        > rails generate migration migration_description
        > rails db:seed
        > rails db:rollback (undo last migration)

    - Generate

        > rails generate controller Posts
        > rails g controller home --skip-javascripts
        > rails generate model Post
        > rails generate model Post name: string title: string content: text
        > rails destroy model Post

        - Destroy :
        
        rails d controller lalala
        rails d model yadayada
        rails d scaffold hohoho



